        "type": "university",
        "description": "The Haute École de Commerce de Kinshasa (commonly abbreviated as HEC-Kin), formerly known as Institut Supérieur de Commerce de Kinshasa (ISC-Kin), is a public technical university strategically located on Avenue de la Déliberation in the Batetela neighborhood of Gombe, Kinshasa. Specializing in commerce and related disciplines, the institution focuses on training professionals in commercial, technical, accounting, and computer science fields to support national development. Its academic programs comprise general education courses, specialized technical and commercial training, and advanced courses tailored to each area of specialization."
